metadata.name: Sun Edition – Justice
metadata.description:
RELIX – Sun Edition

Justice

Libra nature. Continuing from the Wheel of Fortune’s energy; when one persists in attempting to distort the Wheel’s turning, a need for Justice energy is the result. Often, this energy may appear as cold & unfeeling – but this is only when viewed from a single perspective. The key to harnessing Justice spirit is understanding a higher octave of reason. When one steps outside their own viewpoint to determine a greater balance for the universe, true Justice is realized.

Designed by Jiminie Ha & Jeremy Parker 
Text by Michael George Land 
More info at wolfhouse.art
